          <h3>9. Doug Barth said...</h3>
          <div class="body"><p>After countless times of accidentally hitting the &#8216;q&#8217; key and enabling recording mode, I finally read up on it and found it immensely useful for complex repetitive tasks. q&lt;letter> starts recording into a named register. @&lt;letter> replays the actions you did. Priceless once you start using it.</p></div>
