          <h3>13. Rich said...</h3>
          <div class="body"><p>Re: the file count ceiling of 10000 files&#8230; (comment #11 above), you can change the ceiling in the fuzzyfinder_textmate.vim file (line 39):</p>


	<p>ruby def finder; @finder ||= FuzzyFileFinder.new(&#8221;.&#8221;,50000); end</p></div>
        </div>
        
