          <h3>18. frew said...</h3>
          <div class="body"><p>awesome vim features (for me:)</p>


	<p>ciw, ci&#8217;, cit (html tags) which are of course related to the viw you mentioned in your post.</p>


	<p>splits!  ^w ^s will split horizontally, ^w ^v will do vertically and then ^w (h,j,k,l) will move among the splits and if you do a shift on those it will move the split you are in in that direction.</p></div>
