          <h3>77. Stephen Waits said...</h3>
          <div class="body"><p>@Mike.. I set files which are readonly (in the filesystem) to be non-modifiable buffers like this:</p>


	<p>&#8221; set modifiable state of buffer to match readonly state (unless overridden
&#8221; manually)
function UpdateModifiable() 
    if &#38;readonly 
        setlocal nomodifiable 
    else 
        setlocal modifiable 
    endif 
endfunction</p>


	<p>autocmd BufReadPost * call UpdateModifiable()</p></div>
        </div>
        
