          <h3>159. Jamis said...</h3>
          <div class="body"><p>@AdulteratedJedi, I&#8217;m afraid I&#8217;ve no idea why that&#8217;s happening. If you figure it out, please post an update.</p>


	<p>@flevour, you can refresh the index by issuing this vim command:</p>


<table class="CodeRay"><tr>
  <td title="click to toggle" class="line_numbers"><pre><tt>
</tt></pre></td>
  <td class="code"><pre>:ruby finder.rescan!</pre></td>
</tr></table>


	<p>I need to package that in a more sane vim function, but in the meantime it&#8217;s not hard to map that to something yourself.</p></div>
