	<p>mvim&#8212;remote-send &#8217;:ruby finder.rescan!&lt;cr>&#8216;</p>


	<p>Just trying to create a Daemon to watch for files/dir and send that command when there are new ones.</p>


	<p>Should make for a better textmate like experience :-)</p></div>
